Now, it&#8217;s my turn. Turning the pungent onions into to sweet caramel. YEAH BABY!!!</p>
<p>But I don&#8217;t eat beef. What&#8217;s a poor girl to do???<br />
What do you think about chicken stock and a big dash of Worcestershire???<br />
(Julia is rolling over in her grave, I&#8217;m sure of it!) </p>
<p>Bon Appétit!</p>
	</li>
		
		
		
	
